{"tid":885771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"非洲最小爭執島 半個足球場大住500人","createTime":"2018-11-01T14:56:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T16:09:27.000Z","uid":28765,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f890ab93f2da564db9656c0710aa1052a5856c9a","tid":885771,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T14:56:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php51YEr8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php51YEr8.jpg&h=d9d322c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「Migingo」島面積只有足球場一半，島上居民每人僅有1坪多生活空間。（法新社）<br />\n2018-11-01 12:34<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpCTAI3J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpCTAI3J.jpg&h=5aa6de2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n島上居民的住家有許多都房屋重疊，生活環境相當狹隘。（法新社）<br />\n〔影音新聞／綜合報導〕非洲有一座小漁島，漁島面積僅有足球場的一半，但當地人口相當稠密，島上住家更有許多房屋重疊，每人平均生活空間更僅有1坪，人民生活在如此狹隘的空間中，讓人難以置信。<br />\n綜合外媒報導，該做小漁島名為「Migingo」，位於烏干達和肯亞邊境交界的維多利亞湖中，面積僅2000平方米（約605坪），卻有約500位居民，每人平均只有4平方米（約1坪）的生活空間。<br />\n《紐西蘭先驅報》報導，「Migingo」島四面環湖，居民以捕魚為經濟基礎，該島被稱作「非洲最小的爭執地」，因位置處於維多利亞湖中部，使得鄰國烏干達及肯亞都聲稱擁有主權，烏干達率先宣布該島成為海盜的避風港，並開始對該島的漁民進行監管及徵稅。<br />\n對於「Migingo」島的主權問題，居住在島上、22歲的烏干達人Isaac Buhinza表示，我不知道這個島屬於哪個國家，我只想在這裡好好生活；肯亞漁民Emmanuel Aringo說，這都是政治問題，我只想好好的賣魚生活；一名當地的肯亞警察說道：「島上長期以來都只放烏干達的國旗，9月中有肯亞人試圖舉起肯亞國旗時，造成嚴重的爭執。」<br />\n據了解，「Migingo」島上除了住家、漁船等房屋，妓院也相當多，因位於烏干達和肯亞邊境交界，許多不同國籍的漁民都在到島上消費，使得當地的賣淫現象十分普遍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2598608\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2598608&d=rhwCuyOkgID7OebO1yMOFnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=433c9e6e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2598608&h=ff54e990\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2598608</a><br />\n<br />\n細過香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea45cf1c71290e1351df0becde624802594e34b","tid":885771,"uid":46896,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T15:21:33.000Z","msg":"我地鴨脷州仲勁啦"},{"pid":"4ac8fa610d9a42030b13f0cb5d86269bee3614bf","tid":885771,"uid":20058,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T15:26:55.000Z","msg":"2歲的烏干達人Isaac Buhinza表示，我不知道這個島屬於哪個國家，我只想在這裡好好生活；肯亞漁民Emmanuel Aringo說，這都是政治問題，我只想好好的賣魚生活；<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同班香港人一撚樣"},{"pid":"45c0ce871c3f0dc2b8e457fd402abfa8a5d75b93","tid":885771,"uid":174530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T15:30:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4edb72593f749c2754cd534e8aded54dee4f6b01","tid":885771,"uid":69213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T15:35:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a35a335d5fc42ec0419489c96473343e4401e1af","tid":885771,"uid":46947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T15:40:50.000Z","msg":"打風一定好刺激<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec816c98d5adf2e107ea09a87ad18e2635d3b2f7","tid":885771,"uid":6799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a35a335d5fc42ec0419489c96473343e4401e1af","tid":885771,"uid":46947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T15:40:50.000Z","msg":"打風一定好刺激<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T15:45:58.000Z","msg":"湖中間 應該少打風"},{"pid":"5c6232d9d89ade9c0a4ec22ecb22c13952ecd8b5","tid":885771,"uid":49392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTi